title: Head to Kysuce and fall in love with Slovakia (again)
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
The Kysuce region is a quintessential Slovak region, with quaint hilltop villages and plenty of adventures to offer. 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec 
Guests: Mirka Petríková, Avuzwa Ngubo, Pedro Viola de Abreu
